Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.70,0:00:24.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あたしも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.85,0:00:27.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃあね　アカネちゃん　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.01,0:00:29.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,また明日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.34,0:00:45.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だぁれ　一緒に遊ばな…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:14.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,日が暮れる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:21.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,家に帰らなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.99,0:01:25.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここはどこ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:38.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,早く家に帰らなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:53.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やれやれ　日の暮れるのが早くなったな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.16,0:02:11.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,本当にこっちでいいんだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:16.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,安心おしよ　大丈夫だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.81,0:02:17.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうだか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:22.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だいたいばあさん　なんであんな所にいたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:28.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それがねぇ　どうしてだかねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:34.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おーい　ばあさんやーい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.53,0:02:41.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ばあさん　みかげやーい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:43.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じいさんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.09,0:02:48.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おーい　陽吉さん　こっちだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:58.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,本当に　なんとお礼を言えば良いか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.70,0:03:01.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,途中でとんでもないもの拾ったと思いましたがね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:06.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ご苦労かけましたな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:09.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,わしは少々足が悪いでな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:12.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんな奥までは　山に入れん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:16.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そなたが通らなかったらと思うと　ぞっとしますわい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.21,0:03:23.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,大したお礼もできませんが　せめて休んでいってください
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:24.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そりゃどうも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:30.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,しかし　なぜ山に入ったのか分からないでは心配ですな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:37.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれはこの頃　たまにこういう事がありましてな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:45.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,夕方になると　今日のような夕焼けの日なんかは特に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:49.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,帰ると言って　家を出ようとするのですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:57.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,年を取ると　稀にそう言い出す者がいるとは聞いた事があるが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:02.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,子供の頃の記憶に　一時的に戻ってしまうとか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:08.23,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その頃の家に　帰ろうとしているのかもしれませんな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:13.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まぁ　わしもあやつも長く生きた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:16.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あちこちガタがくるのも当然だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:21.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,また　そうやって人の事もうろく扱いして
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:24.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,本当の事だろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:28.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,私ゃまだあんたよりよっぽど働きますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.21,0:04:32.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そっちこそ一人じゃ飯も炊けないくせして
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:35.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,私がいなくなったらどうすんのかね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:37.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何を偉そうに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:40.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もうろく言われたくなかったらしっかりしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:43.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お客の前で　でかい声出すんじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.14,0:04:44.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どっちがだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:49.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんた　蟲師なのかい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:53.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,昔この里にもいたねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:58.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,娘の疳の蟲やらイネの病気やらで世話になったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:00.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだったなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:10.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これで膝が治るって？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:11.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:22.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そう言やなんか楽になったな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:24.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,本当かい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.41,0:05:28.78,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,明日の朝　もう一度すれば完治するはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:32.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そいつはありがたい　
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:34.44,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,恩に着る
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:52.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ギンコさんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:02.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ばあさんのことだがね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:08.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,年を取って　子供の頃の事を思い出すというのは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:12.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,昔の記憶を無くした者にもあるのかね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.21,0:06:15.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,さぁ　そこまでは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:20.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.35,0:06:23.41,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ばあさん　記憶が無いのかい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:25.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,0:06:31.14,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれは昔　突如この里に現れたのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:36.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,普段はもう　そんなことを忘れてしまっているのだがな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:42.22,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だが　ふと思い返すたび　
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:51.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれは一体なんだったのだろうと　思うのだよ
