Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:17.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まだ帰んないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:20.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,父ちゃんが畑から帰るの待ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:25.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そっか　あんま暗くなる前に帰れよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:27.03,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:29.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃあな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:31.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,うん　また明日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:39.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,こんばんは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:43.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,うちのアカネ来てないかい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:44.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:49.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,陽吉　お前知らないかい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:54.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,アカネ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:56.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,アカネちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:01.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,アカネ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:11.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,誰だ　お前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.37,0:08:18.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,アカネは　それきり姿を消した
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:22.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,名前は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:28.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,里はどこだい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:30.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だろうね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:33.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ちょっと気味が悪いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:37.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ありゃ　鬼の子じゃあるまいか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:41.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃあアカネちゃんは　鬼に食われちまったってのかい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:43.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,しっ　およしよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:55.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やがて　その子を引き取ると名乗り出たのは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:57.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,アカネの父だった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.19,0:09:06.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,考えてみりゃ　あの子もかわいそうなもんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:11.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,健気なもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:20.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの子　遊びにまざってこないね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.61,0:09:22.06,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,つまんない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:31.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:34.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前　アカネの真似すんなよな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:44.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あたしだってこんなのしたくないわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:49.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　お義父さんがくれたんだから仕方ないじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:53.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,するしかないじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.42,0:09:59.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,こっ　こら　みかげ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:06.58,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やがて　みかげは里に溶け込んでいった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:13.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そして　時が過ぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:18.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やがてわしらは夫婦となった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:24.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,共に子を育てあげ　共に老い
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:31.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,このまま　この里に共に骨を埋めるのだと
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:33.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,当然のように思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.19,0:10:44.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,夕方になるたび　帰るなどと言い出すまでは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:49.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,妙な話だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:57.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ばあさんは　自分の故郷の事をいつか思い出すのかもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:05.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうしたら　やはり帰りたいと思うのかのう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:11.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,夕暮れ時に　人が入れ替わる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:18.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それと同じ現象を聞いた事がある
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.48,0:11:25.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,夕暮れ時にのみ現世に現れる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.32,0:11:28.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,「大禍時」というものがある
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:32.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それにのまれた者は　
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:37.43,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,夕暮れ時　本体の無い影のみの姿で現れる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:45.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そして　その影に踏まれたり踏んだりすると
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:48.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,影の本体と入れ替わりに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.21,0:11:51.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,大禍時にのまれてしまう　
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:54.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,…のだろうと考えられている
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:12:01.67,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何せ　そうやって現れた者は そこまでの記憶が無くなっているため　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:03.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,実証は無い
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:11.13,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　アカネはみかげと入れ違えに…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:17.77,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なら　アカネはその後　どうなったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:19.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,さあな　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:23.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　同じように誰かと入れ替わって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:26.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どこかで暮らしているんじゃないだろうかね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:30.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どこに現れたかは分からんのか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:36.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,大禍時は現世とは別の所にあるという
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.07,0:12:39.98,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いつ　どこでつながるかは分からん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:43.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.15,0:12:52.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,アカネも　どこかで幸せになってくれてるといいが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:14.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう飽きちゃった　綾取りしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:25.27,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねぇ　影踏みの続きしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:37.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんた　誰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:47.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いやぁ　お陰ですっかりよくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:48.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そりゃよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:54.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そういや　同じような足の悪い連中が数人いてな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:57.08,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ついでに診てやっちゃくれんか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:14:01.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんならもう一日いてくれてもいいしの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:03.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃ　そうさせてもらうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:13.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ばあさん　ギンコさんに食わせる魚でも捕ってくるわい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:19.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうかい　膝が治ったからって無理すんじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:21.86,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,分かっとるわい　
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:24.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,夕方までにゃ戻るからな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:29.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,はいはい　いってらっしゃい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:35.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,膝から何か出たぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:38.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　楽になったな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:41.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,うちのじいさんのも…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:42.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これはただの痣ですな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.34,0:14:51.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おーい　戻ったぞ　
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:54.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,大漁じゃわい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:14:59.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ばあさん？
