Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:12.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まだ日も高い　少し家を空けただけじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:14.26,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,提灯がないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:20.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あいつ　とうとう故郷を思い出したのかもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.12,0:15:23.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それで…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:50.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここはどこなの　
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:54.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,誰もいない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:16:00.51,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いつまでも　夕暮れのまま
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:04.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,寂しい　
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.07,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,寂しい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.06,0:16:12.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,怖い
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:17.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,きっと　
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:20.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの影のせいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:26.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの影が私の影を踏んだから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:30.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.18,0:16:33.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,うん　また明日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.03,0:16:44.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だぁれ　
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.07,0:16:45.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一緒に遊ばな…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.81,0:16:55.72,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの影が私の影を踏んだから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:01.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:06.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ごめんね　アカネちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.19,0:17:17.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれか
