Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:30.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前　一体どういう…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:39.05,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,思い出した…のか
