Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:04.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんたやお義父さんに会えて幸せだった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:13.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　わたしはあそこにいていい子じゃなかったの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:21.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,わたし　アカネちゃんを身代わりにしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:28.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,わたしと入れ替わればいいと思って　
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:30.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,影を踏んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:39.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そして　あの子の全部を盗んだの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.54,0:18:43.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ごめんね　
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:53.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんたからアカネちゃんを奪ってごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:02.15,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,わしには謝らんでくれんか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:11.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,わしも幸せだったよ　
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:15.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ずっと　ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.96,0:19:22.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前のお陰での
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.90,0:19:33.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,さあ　帰ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:40.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,わしらの家に帰ろう
