Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:56.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,流行病でばあさんが亡くなるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:19:59.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,二人は幸せに暮らしたという
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.59,0:20:09.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だが…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:22.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,アカネ？
