Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:28.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,わしだ　陽吉だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.59,0:20:35.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前　どうして　ずっとそのままで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.91,0:20:43.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうか　お前　踏めなかったんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:53.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ひどく心根の優しい娘だったもんな
