Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.29,0:21:22.92,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なら　わしの影を踏んでくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:27.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,頼む　アカネ　戻ってきてくれ
